 {"text": "$", "bbox": [511.6, 478.7, 519.7, 493.3]}, {"text": "460", "bbox": [547.9, 478.7, 572.2, 493.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [594.3, 478.7, 602.4, 493.3]}, {"text": "(25)", "bbox": [637.3, 478.7, 660.5, 493.3]}, {"text": "(5)%", "bbox": [731.4, 478.7, 759.5, 493.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [787.3, 478.7, 795.4, 493.3]}, {"text": "460", "bbox": [823.7, 478.7, 848.0, 493.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [892.0, 478.7, 900.2, 493.3]}, {"text": "430", "bbox": [928.4, 478.7, 952.8, 493.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [970.8, 478.7, 978.9, 493.3]}, {"text": "30", "bbox": [1013.8, 478.7, 1030.0, 493.3]}, {"text": "7%", "bbox": [1104.5, 478.7, 1125.6, 493.3]}, {"text": "(1)", "bbox": [162.5, 529.1, 179.8, 545.8]}, {"text": "Includes the operating results of AMR Research and Burton Group, which we purchased in December 2009. The results of", "bbox": [197.2, 529.1, 1087.3, 545.8]}, {"text": "these businesses were not material to our 2009 segment results.", "bbox": [197.2, 551.4, 666.7, 568.1]}, {"text": "(2)", "bbox": [162.5, 597.3, 179.8, 613.9]}, {"text": "Dollars in thousands.", "bbox": [197.2, 597.3, 348.8, 613.9]}, {"text": "(3)", "bbox": [162.5, 643.1, 179.8, 659.8]}, {"text": "Excludes AMR Research and Burton Group.", "bbox": [197.2, 643.1, 517.5, 659.8]}, {"text": "2009 VERSUS 2008", "bbox": [162.5, 689.3, 332.1, 708.0]}, {"text": "Consulting revenues declined 17% when comparing 2009 with 2008, with the majority of the decline in core consulting, and to a", "bbox": [162.5, 714.0, 1093.6, 730.6]}, {"text": "lesser extent, in our SAS and contract optimization businesses. The decline in core consulting was driven by lower headcount,", "bbox": [162.5, 738.3, 1077.1, 755.0]}, {"text": "utilization, and billing rates. The decline in revenue in our contract optimization business reflects a large contract received at the", "bbox": [162.5, 762.6, 1083.4, 779.3]}, {"text": "end of 2008 which was not repeated in 2009. SAS revenues declined due to approximately 17% fewer fulfilled SAS days.", "bbox": [162.5, 787.0, 1041.6, 803.6]}, {"text": "Excluding the unfavorable impact of foreign currency, overall Consulting revenues were down about 15%.", "bbox": [162.5, 811.3, 924.3, 828.0]}, {"text": "The 2 point decline in the Consulting contribution margin reflects lower revenue in our SAS and contract optimization businesses,", "bbox": [162.5, 859.2, 1097.3, 875.9]}, {"text": "which have higher margins than core consulting. To a lesser extent, the decline also reflects lower utilization and billing rates in", "bbox": [162.5, 883.6, 1076.8, 900.2]}, {"text": "core consulting.", "bbox": [162.5, 907.9, 277.2, 924.6]}, {"text": "We ended 2009 with 442 billable consultants, a decline of 11% from the prior year end as we tightly managed resources to match", "bbox": [162.5, 955.9, 1106.4, 972.5]}, {"text": "demand. The decline reflects normal attrition as well as the termination of approximately 30 consultants in January 2009 to better", "bbox": [162.5, 980.2, 1098.1, 996.8]}, {"text": "align our delivery resources with lower backlog.", "bbox": [162.5, 1004.5, 504.2, 1021.2]}, {"text": "Consulting backlog declined 6% year-over-year but increased 7% sequentially in the fourth quarter of 2009 to $90.9 million, as", "bbox": [162.5, 1052.5, 1077.8, 1069.1]}, {"text": "demand for our consulting services was solid in the U.S. while demand in Europe lagged.", "bbox": [162.5, 1076.8, 810.0, 1093.5]}, {"text": "2008 VERSUS 2007", "bbox": [162.5, 1123.1, 332.1, 1141.9]}, {"text": "Consulting revenues increased year-over-year by $22.4 million, or 7%. Excluding the favorable impact of foreign currency", "bbox": [162.5, 1147.7, 1036.2, 1164.3]}, {"text": "translation, revenues for 2008 were up about 6%. The revenue increase was due to strength in both the core consulting and", "bbox": [162.5, 1172.0, 1063.3, 1188.7]}, {"text": "benchmarking businesses and exceptionally strong results in our contract optimization business. Contributing to the year-over-year", "bbox": [162.5, 1196.3, 1106.9, 1213.0]}, {"text": "revenue increase in our contract optimization business was the completion of one large contract in the fourth quarter of 2008", "bbox": [162.5, 1220.8, 1068.4, 1237.4]}, {"text": "which resulted in approximately $11.0 million of revenue.", "bbox": [162.5, 1245.1, 572.3, 1261.8]}, {"text": "Consulting gross contribution increased by $13.1 million while the gross contribution margin improved by 2 points. These", "bbox": [162.5, 1293.1, 1038.7, 1309.7]}, {"text": "improvements were driven by improved utilization on higher headcount and higher billing rates, and higher revenues in our contract", "bbox": [162.5, 1317.4, 1109.9, 1334.1]}, {"text": "optimization business, which has a higher margin than our core consulting business.", "bbox": [162.5, 1341.7, 773.2, 1358.4]}, {"text": "Consulting backlog, which represents future revenues to be recognized from in-process consulting, measurement and SAS, was", "bbox": [162.5, 1389.7, 1091.6, 1406.3]}, {"text": "$97.2 million at December 31, 2008, compared to $121.4 million at December 31, 2007, as bookings slowed in the fourth quarter", "bbox": [162.5, 1414.0, 1104.8, 1430.7]}, {"text": "of 2008 due to the weaker economic environment.", "bbox": [162.5, 1438.3, 529.1, 1455.0]}, {"text": "21", "bbox": [1094.1, 1499.3, 1112.7, 1515.9]}]}